==English==
===Verb form===
'''stocking'''

#Present participle of '''to [[stock]]'''.
#: ''I've almost finished stocking these groceries.''

===Verbal noun===
'''stocking''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#The action of the verb '''to stock'''.

===Noun===
'''stocking''' (''plural'' '''[[stockings]]''')

#A soft garment worn on the foot and lower leg, worn under shoes or other [[footwear]].

====Usage notes====
*'''Stocking''' may refer either to men's socks or to women's [[hose]], but rarely to socks when worn by women.  However, this usage appears somewhat variable.

====Derived terms====
*[[in one's stockinged feet]]

